Uttar Pradesh
Nov 17, 2014
Murder, Crime
Description:
			A six-year-old handicapped girl was shot dead allegedly by some persons in Madanpur area.

The incident took place yesterday when the accused Om Prakash, Munna and Pintu opened fire on Sripal Yadav, in which his grand-daughter was killed.

The minor girl died on the spot.

The incident was stated to be fallout of old enmity over land dispute.


